General.Name: United Medical Group CY PLC
General.Description: United Medical Group CY PLC provides healthcare services under the European Medical Center (EMC) brand name in Russia. It operates clinics in areas, such as children's, sports traumatology and orthopedics, oncology, gynecology and oncogynecology, dermatovenereology and allergology-immunology, weight correction, pain management, mammology, neurology and neurosurgery, otorhinolaryngology, head and neck surgery, ophthalmology, plastic surgery, psychiatry and psychotherapy, reproductive and prenatal medicine, heart and vascular, tropical medicine, ambulance and emergency department, maternity hospital, dental, therapeutic, urology, surgical, and aesthetic clinics, as well as diagnostic and rehabilitation centers, and center for robotic surgery. The company also offers COVID-19 diagnosis, treatment, rehabilitation, and vaccination services. It serves legal entities and individuals. The company was founded in 1989 and is based in Limassol, Cyprus.
